description:
2022 Hewescraft 180 Pro V, Full side Canvas Bimini with top windows, Large bench seats, Extended transom, 26 gallon Fish Box, tow post with utility tray
Powered with Yamaha F150XB Outboard Motor.
Comes on a EzLoader Galvanized Trailer
Financing Available
Whether its a windy day on the lake, a rough morning on the river, or a calm afternoon on the coast, the Pro V is the boat to beat. It rewrites the rules for versatility (and blows the competition out of the water) by taking design cues from Hewescraft's most popular fresh and saltwater models. With a Sportsman silhouette, and a wider hull, deeper V, and a shored up stern with an extended transom made popular on the big-water Sea Runner and Ocean Pro models.
